  27 Jun 2005; Marcelo Goes <vanquirius@gentoo.org> bmon-2.0.1.ebuild:
  amd64 stable.

  24 Apr 2005; Marcelo Goes <vanquirius@gentoo.org> -bmon-1.2.1.ebuild:
  Removing old version. Note that there is a 2.1.0 version available, but I am
  not bumping it since I could not get it to compile.

  07 Mar 2005; Gustavo Zacarias <gustavoz@gentoo.org> bmon-2.0.1.ebuild:
